            <Paragraph style={{ fontSize: 13 }}>• Severity-colored cards: 🔴 Critical (&gt;5% projected increase), 🟡 Warning (&gt;2%), 🟢 Stable — showing current error rate, projected rate, and trend per hour</Paragraph>
