        <Paragraph><Strong>LCP</Strong> (good ≤2.5s), <Strong>CLS</Strong> (good ≤0.1), <Strong>INP</Strong> (good ≤200ms), <Strong>TTFB</Strong> (good ≤800ms).</Paragraph>
